@startuml
title Use Case D - Candidate Rank Flow
skinparam shadowing false

start
:BusinessSystem\ncall POST rank\n(candidates + optional strategy);
note right
  **No** Index / Vector / Feature\nadapter calls — pure scoring.
end note
if (strategy == **ctr_first** ?) then (yes)
  :final_score = 0.2×base_score\n+ 0.7×ctr_score\n+ 0.1×freshness_score;
elseif (strategy == **fresh_first** ?) then (yes)
  :final_score = 0.2×base_score\n+ 0.2×ctr_score\n+ 0.6×freshness_score;
else (**hybrid** or any other name)
  :final_score = 0.5×base_score\n+ 0.3×ctr_score\n+ 0.2×freshness_score;
endif
:Attach **final_score** per item\n(read base_score, ctr_score,\nfreshness_score; default 0);
:Sort by final_score descending;
:Return **items**, **count**, **strategy**;
stop
@enduml
